{"tid":1451392,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"我由聽日開始會Full Gear返工","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:58:51.000Z","uid":27238,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d688732ab257dd436b5ade60d8b8f97366973f1","tid":1451392,"uid":27238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:30.000Z","msg":"今晚係好悲痛既一天<br />\n<br />\n無力感好重<br />\n<br />\n我返到屋企望住電視望住Facebook<br />\n<br />\n睇到個女仔既消息 睇到各處警暴<br />\n<br />\n我真係有種心酸想喊既感覺<br />\n<br />\n我諗 除左六日企出黎外 <br />\n<br />\n閒時返工都要做一d野去支持大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由聽日開始 我每日都會Full Gear返工 背脊貼住張紙分享我既感受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反正d紙咁易爛 每日用A3寫d唔同既野都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫大家都咁做 而係想帶出 我地閒時都可以做多d 每個人都做多d 我地既香港都會更好<br />\n<br />\n原諒我既後知後覺 我知好多兄弟一早應該咁做緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港   時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb46609bb52d5660ef1bcca5a05198e99428274e","tid":1451392,"uid":220463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:24.000Z","msg":"保護好自己 就係最好既幫忙<br />\n小心為上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日有好多人都訓唔到<br />\n我識個女仔 ，知道個下心痛到尼，人品好 樣又唔差而家咁樣除咗毁容仲有可能俾人拉去坐監，而家仲做緊手術生死未卜，又唔知佢醒返之後會點 佢嘅人生仲好長依家先行咗&frac14;<br />\n但尼啲全部都係佢為呢場運動付出嘅嘢<br />\n我地冇辦法去彌補佢<br />\n但我地可以用自己嘅方法令佢嘅受傷變得更有價值<br />\n 唔好令佢嘅付出白白浪費，呢場仗一定要贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee09dcc743453dac9cf6aaee1e37dbb38f4e44d2","tid":1451392,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:15.000Z","msg":"跟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通<br />\n無人落charge<br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6.疑似洗頭艇<br />\n（突發推上熱門）洗頭艇 被捕示威者被送到新屋嶺拘留中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446427</a><br />\n<br />\n香港811 back-up 影片 List<br />\n插贓嫁禍<br />\n太古近距離開槍 人踩人<br />\n警黑合作打記者 冇拉到人<br />\n示威者被打到頭破血流<br />\n黑警扮示威者做卧底<br />\n荃灣綠楊白衫打人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=bca09939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8</a>"},{"pid":"4785a1de129eea4c8974ebee5dee0ebcecef0568","tid":1451392,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03d561dc25fa4764e04a8215e09996055a2577fe","tid":1451392,"uid":228888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"Be Water Be Humble"},{"pid":"8aead8f0f112d74bcfae912965223a34762404cb","tid":1451392,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7f5d2c6612ae07db86f9ef06dd098c1828ab7b9","tid":1451392,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb25ba5d434de4c7727dea81ac9345d62f397165","tid":1451392,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50ec306d35e1e9e598125f516e9bd0741c290747","tid":1451392,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85ba7334eaf78a4150c8cd9339815d77bd80c803","tid":1451392,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:51.000Z","msg":"返咩工先？"},{"pid":"3f3897068327a1384d03d81cbf2d4fa720124552","